<doc id="1084323" wikidata="Q1080197" url="?curid=1084323" title="Kotipelto">
<text>Kotipelto is a Finnish power metal self-named band by Timo Kotipelto, created during a hiatus in activity for power metal band Stratovarius. Kotipelto has been commercially well received in their native Finland, with a top 10 single &quot;Beginning&quot; from his first release &quot;Waiting for the Dawn&quot;, and lyrics often concentrating on ancient Egyptian themes.

== Discography ==
=== Albums ===
*2002: &quot;Waiting for the Dawn&quot;
*2004: &quot;Coldness&quot;
*2007: &quot;Serenity&quot;

=== Singles ===
*2002: &quot;Beginning&quot;
*2004: &quot;Reasons&quot;
*2004: &quot;Take Me Away&quot;
*2006: &quot;Sleep Well&quot;

== Members ==
